data.description: ASSUMABLE VA MORTGAGE AT 5.3%!!  AND FURNISHED!! Low down payment required and assume this low interest rate mortgage on beautiful young Shea Built ARIA villa.  NO CDD!  Beautiful and in demand wood plank style tile throughout living area and upgraded textured carpeting in the 2 bedrooms.  Bring in the grays or the beiges as the color palette works well with either.                                            36" cabinets with crown and light rail trim on the bottom and under cabinet lighting.                                    Master bathroom shower has upgraded tile and dual sinks.                    SMART HOME features.
